<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>yé sū kū le 迦南1101</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 yé sū kū le yīn wèi dì xiōng xì gàn qiáng. yé sū kū le yīn wèi shén de diàn huāng liáng.
 yé sū kū le yīn wèi wú rén xún zhǎo mí yáng. shéi néng tǐ tiē zhǔ de xīn cháng.
 dì xiōng a wǒ men yào bǐ cǐ qiān ràng. dì xiōng a wǒ men yào bǐ cǐ qiān ràng.
 duō shǎo gè yè wǎn yé sū wèi nǐ shǒu wàng. tā de xīn jí qí yōu shāng.</lyrics>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>1101</hymn_number>
</song>